reagent-name-cocaine = cocaine
reagent-desc-cocaine = A fine powdered stimulant that makes you far more alert. Helps you stay awake and focused, at the cost of severe damage to your kidneys, liver, heart and respiratory system, as well as being heavily addictive. Resist Cocaine.

reagent-name-crack = crack cocaine
reagent-desc-crack = A crystalized form of cocaine that is far more potent and addictive than it's powdered form. Helps you stay awake and focused for much longer, at the cost of extreme damage to your kidneys, liver, heart, respiratory system and brain function. It is rumored that this drug is used to destabilize native populations on planets that Nanotrasen wishes to colonize.

reagent-name-cocaslurry = coca slurry
reagent-desc-cocaslurry = A slurry made from grinding coca leaves. Nowhere nearly as stimulating as it's refined counterparts.
